#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&skladnik; is copyright &copy; 1998-2000 by &Anders.Widell; &Anders.Widell."
"mail;."
msgstr ""
"Авторські права на &skladnik; належать &Anders.Widell; &Anders.Widell.mail;, "
"1998–2000."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The background graphics <quote>starfield</quote> was taken from the <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.gimp.org/\">Gimp</ulink>. All other graphics were created "
"by &Anders.Widell; &Anders.Widell.mail; using the <ulink url=\"https://www."
"povray.org/\">Povray</ulink> ray tracer."
msgstr ""
"Графічні елементи тла, <quote>зоряне поле</quote>, було запозичено з <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.gimp.org/\">Gimp</ulink>. Усі інші графічні елементи було "
"створено &Anders.Widell; &Anders.Widell.mail; за допомогою програми <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.povray.org/\">Povray</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
